WEBVTT

00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:33.336
Kwa hiyo maboresho mengi ya elimu 
yanaendeshwa na mtazamo wa kihuruma

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:34.616
ambapo watu wanasema

00:02:34.640 --> 00:02:37.656
"Twende tukasaidie hawa watoto maskini 
wa ndani ndani ya jiji

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:39.680
au hawa watoto maskini weusi na wakilatino

00:02:40.320 --> 00:02:42.696
badala ya mtazamo wa uelewa,

00:02:42.720 --> 00:02:46.136
ambapo mtu ka' mimi, aliyekulia
katika mazingira haya, ningeweza kusema,

00:02:46.160 --> 00:02:48.376
"Najua taabu mnazokumbana nazo

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:50.240
na ninataka kuwasaidia kuzishinda."

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:54.276
Leo nipatapo maswali kuhusu 
jinsi nilivyofanikiwa kutoka,

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:56.776
Natoa sababu moja wapo kubwa

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:58.880
kuwa sikuwa na aibu kuomba msaada.

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:02.456
Katika tabaka la hali ya kati 
au kaya tajiri,